channel.title: AP News - US News
channel.description: Top US News stories from AP News

item.title: Arizona Democratic campaign office damaged by gunfire
item.description: Authorities say someone fired shots at a Democratic Party campaign office in a Phoenix suburb, causing damage but no injuries.

item.title: New York resident dies of rare mosquito-borne virus known as eastern equine encephalitis
item.description: A person has died in New York state from eastern equine encephalitis. The death was reported Monday in Ulster County.

item.title: FBI: Son of suspect in Trump assassination attempt arrested on child sexual abuse images charges
item.description: The son of the man suspected in the assassination attempt in Florida of former President Donald Trump has been arrested on charges of possessing child sexual abuse images.
